org.cloudbus.cloudsim.util

Interface DataCloudTags


  • public interface DataCloudTags
    Contains additional tags for the DataCloud functionalities, such as file information retrieval, file transfers, and storage info.
    Since:
    CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
    Author:
    Uros Cibej, Anthony Sulistio

        Denotes the request to modify an existing master file information stored in the Replica Catalogue.

        The format of this request is Object[3] = {String filename, FileAttribute attr, Integer resID}.

        The reply tag name is CTLG_MODIFY_MASTER_RESULT.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • CTLG_MODIFY_MASTER_RESULT

        static final int CTLG_MODIFY_MASTER_RESULT
        Sends the result of modifying a master file back to sender.

        The format of the reply is Object[2] = {String lfn, Integer resultID}.

        NOTE: The result id is in the form of CTLG_MODIFY_MASTER_XXXX where XXXX means the error/success message
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • CTLG_MODIFY_MASTER_SUCCESSFUL

        static final int CTLG_MODIFY_MASTER_SUCCESSFUL
